{"tid":1021160,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀讚記","createTime":"2019-02-14T05:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T06:32:27.000Z","uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2eecefa7248684ebaf5f6698fe16a9b4026555ce","tid":1021160,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:27:40.000Z","msg":"呢間唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n枱大，一湯一茶碟頭飯，四十幾。<br />\n<br />\n湯OKAY，茶正常，飯份量不錯。<br />\n<br />\n先頭食個咸蛋肉餅飯，味道唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n平時買其他快餐，咸到爆／勁重味精，讚記呢間有水準噃。"},{"pid":"bc6ffc04c0e68e754f21313333658ce16e1caa81","tid":1021160,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"寶鞡巷？"},{"pid":"f4e28e9a54f737c64374fb621314534ae7179577","tid":1021160,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:28:20.000Z","msg":"寶勒巷"},{"pid":"865751934d7878ab2b11f60eed6ca7efeab082f5","tid":1021160,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8aef70fc6261467fe3387352c7f984610407949","tid":1021160,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"865751934d7878ab2b11f60eed6ca7efeab082f5","tid":1021160,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"有無其他推介，食過幾間，呢間算唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n試過有間，唔記得鋪名，午餐餐牌喺電視機播出嚟，好似廣告咁Loop。"}]}